title: Pictures To Exe + Reg
description:
This is a handy little program which makes great slideshows and screensavers.

It&#039;s easy to use, just install, load key (which is in here as well), click ok, when it has finished loading, close it down and re-open it.

It may register it in my name, but don&#039;t worry, i won&#039;t tell if you don&#039;t.

The key is also for further upgrades, so keep checking.

Experiment with the program, you can add as many pics/photos as you like, and as much music (if wanted) as you want.

All in all, it&#039;s great for making slideshows, and it makes screensavers as well, so you can make a bob or two if you so wish.
